{"id": 470, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于传统习俗，你有啥要吐槽的？", "description": "比如天还热得个半死呢就要贴秋膘了！吓人！", "record_count": 4586, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606145041DZ71bgsUlKCoTJ2a.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-08-07T10:45:49Z", "options": [{"id": 7432, "content": "基本上都有意见", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142935}, {"id": 7434, "content": "只要放假，我就，喜欢传统节日。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156215}, {"id": 7436, "content": "吃面不得有声音", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155904}, {"id": 7439, "content": "为什么非要结婚生子？不结婚不生孩子又不会死。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156251}, {"id": 8208, "content": "摆酒席", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161432}, {"id": 7444, "content": "作为江南水乡人士，听说某些地区啥节都要吃饺子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493}, {"id": 10010, "content": "被七大姑八大姨品头论足", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172585}, {"id": 10778, "content": "放鞭炮放烟花", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177478}, {"id": 7968, "content": "三伏贴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159817}, {"id": 7459, "content": "亲人去死要哭丧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156335}, {"id": 7463, "content": "求神祈福掷圣杯，掷到满意结果为止", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156383}, {"id": 7477, "content": "除了放鞭炮其他都还好啊 家家户户都放炮好吵啊还污染环境 其实可以以小区街道为单位派个代表放一次就好 听起来就有组织有纪律不吵不闹不骄傲还保护环境人人有责 棒棒嗒", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156492}, {"id": 8246, "content": "我只是想对那个说“过年给压岁钱要磕头，妈蛋21世纪了好吗！”的人说，都21世纪了你还拿什么压岁钱？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161948}, {"id": 7994, "content": "推来搡去的红包", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159569}, {"id": 7488, "content": "媳妇别人家的好，孩子也是比别人家的好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153216}, {"id": 7494, "content": "白事还要大办特办，老人生前对他好点不比这个实在", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156655}, {"id": 7497, "content": "社会发展的速度让我们忘了传统习俗的初心 以后连鞭炮都禁止了可能大家都不知道原来火药是我们发明的了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156715}, {"id": 7498, "content": "他们都是虚岁的忠实不二信奉者。也是说我一回到家就28，其实我也就只有26。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156643}, {"id": 7499, "content": "中国人的奴化教育", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156748}, {"id": 7244, "content": "年初一守财，任何东西不往外扔（包括垃圾）。", "image": null, "praise_count": 110, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 7246, "content": "还这么热呢啊！刚减肥过夏天啊！又要贴秋膘了吗！", "image": null, "praise_count": 107, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 7502, "content": "为什么一过年就要吃水饺！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156812}, {"id": 7248, "content": "每逢佳节必吃一些奇奇怪怪的食物。", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 7504, "content": "？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156838}, {"id": 7509, "content": "人就素这么活该有的过还不懂珍惜没了才知道遗憾", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 7510, "content": "反正只要有假放我管他什么传统的 放假才是正事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 7511, "content": "有些好的习俗应该要传承下去，比如说对联。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146452}, {"id": 8286, "content": "为啥我不能在别人面前评论礼物的好坏啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124369}, {"id": 8287, "content": "大家看啊，什么升学宴啊，乔迁宴啊的，大家把红包送来送去，那，都别送了不是就简单了吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124369}, {"id": 7525, "content": "论性福交流的二次性", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156828}, {"id": 7527, "content": "小时候，总是被问你第几名？长大后，总是被问，你拿多少工资？工作几年后，总是被问，你啥时结婚。妈蛋，我就跟着家里人聚个会，吃个饭，犯得着审犯人一样吗？全国家庭聚会问的问题都一样，都是商量好的要将这个问问题的习俗传承下去吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157087}, {"id": 8346, "content": "别人请你，你还要回请。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162835}, {"id": 7328, "content": "走门探亲 哪些七大姑八大姨啊 烦cry", "image": null, "praise_count": 612, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135605}, {"id": 7329, "content": "闹洞房", "image": null, "praise_count": 525, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149632}, {"id": 7330, "content": "冬至要吃饺子，不然会冻耳朵（吃货给自己找理由也是很努力", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 3797}, {"id": 7331, "content": "徒手杀动物", "image": null, "praise_count": 81, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138437}, {"id": 7333, "content": "拜神烧纸", "image": null, "praise_count": 200, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 56616}, {"id": 7337, "content": "不好玩，习俗什么的都去哪儿了？ 现在连新年都不想过了——虽然我不是大人\n           ", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1064367}, {"id": 7338, "content": "就算生病也不能吃药 坏话反说", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153405}, {"id": 7339, "content": "在路口画个白圈烧纸", "image": null, "praise_count": 92, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 116576}, {"id": 7340, "content": "过年给压岁钱要磕头，妈蛋21世纪了好吗！", "image": null, "praise_count": 127, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 73617}, {"id": 7342, "content": "都还可以，雅人雅风，俗人俗情", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 150050}, {"id": 7598, "content": "敬酒", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135716}, {"id": 7343, "content": "端午吃粽子，粽子真的很难消化好么！！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153786}, {"id": 7344, "content": "反正送红包都是“礼尚往来”，何必这么费事呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 451, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 75648}, {"id": 7345, "content": "总在“下一个节是啥与这个节吃啥”里徘徊", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148846}, {"id": 7348, "content": "可是过节有习俗很好玩啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114367}, {"id": 7349, "content": "明明应该很轻松的团圆饭，还要像准备演讲似的准备祝词向亲戚们敬酒", "image": null, "praise_count": 361, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 58260}, {"id": 7350, "content": "其實我已經忘了傳統習俗了", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 89872}, {"id": 7353, "content": "被不熟的亲戚一顿乱问，感觉什么的简直是醉了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 339, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154704}]}